description: Avast browser security and web reputation plugin.
name: Avast Online Security

permissions.description: Matches any URL that uses the https: scheme.
permissions.name: https://*/*
permissions.warning: Read and change all your data on the websites you visit that uses the scheme https://

permissions.description: Matches any URL that uses the http: scheme.
permissions.name: http://*/*
permissions.warning: Read and change all your data on the websites you visit that uses the scheme http://

permissions.description: Gives your extension access to the chrome.storage API.
permissions.name: storage

permissions.description: Grants the extension access to privileged fields of the Tab objects used by several APIs including chrome.tabs and chrome.windows. In many circumstances the extension will not need to declare the tabs permission to make use of these APIs.
permissions.name: tabs

permissions.description: Grants the extension access to the chrome.webNavigation API.
permissions.name: webNavigation

permissions.description: Gives your extension access to the chrome.webRequest API.
permissions.name: webRequest

permissions.description: Required if the extension uses the chrome.webRequest API in a blocking fashion.
permissions.name: webRequestBlocking
